<para style="q1">

<verse number="18" style="v" />Your thunderous voice was heard in the wind;</para>

<para style="q1">the lightning lit up the world;</para>

<para style="q1">the earth trembled and shook.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="19" style="v" />Your path went through the sea</para>

<para style="q1">and your way through the surging waters,</para>

<para style="q1">but your footprints were not seen.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="20" style="v" />You led your people like a flock</para>

<para style="q1">by the hand of Moses and Aaron.</para>
